ith a color LCD, Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, and an IR transceiver. At the =E2=80=9CH=
ack your badge=E2=80=9D station, attendees flashed new art/games, traded IR=
 messages, and customized firmware. Six apps shipped out of the box: Mona=
=E2=80=99s Quest (track 9 locations), Mona Pet , Mona Sketch , Flappy Mona =
, an image Gallery , and a tracker/settings app.

