=F0=9F=94=A7 Badges, built by Hubbers: a late-night sprint
-----------------------------------------------

Extreme weather caused supply-chain chaos=E2=80=94so Hubbers teamed up with=
 our badge co-creators at Pimoroni> and spent the night assembling units by=
 hand. Thanks to that effort, about 2,500 attendees walked in with hackable=
 badges on Day=C2=A01. Customer-first, community-powered, and a little scra=
ppy=E2=80=94in the best way.

